### ============================================
### Price Tag Reader API
### ============================================

### Переменные
@base_url = http://localhost:8000
@video_id = {{video_id}}


### Health
GET {{base_url}}/health

### Информация о сервисе
GET {{base_url}}/


### Загрузить и обработать видео
POST {{base_url}}/process
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test_video.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

< ./test_data/test_video.mp4
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="frame_interval"

5
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="confidence_threshold"

0.3
--boundary--


### Скачать CSV
GET {{base_url}}/download/{{video_id}}

### Удалить результаты
DELETE {{base_url}}/results/{{video_id}}